<L>__{exterior south carolina shore day}
<A>__{a british packet, a small, fast warship, lies anchored just offshore. a rowboat, manned by half a dozen sailors, carrying a redcoat lieutenant, beaches. several redcoats wait. the lieutenant, carrying a dispatch case, jumps out off the boat, mounts a waiting horse and rides off.}
